{"word":"G911 - βάπτω - báptō - bap'-to - Dip","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">βάπτω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">báptō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">bap'-to</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Dip</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"ஸ்நானம் கொடு"},{"paragraph":"to dip, dip in, immerse"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>A primary verb; to <i>whelm</i>, that is, cover wholly with a fluid; in the New Testament only in a qualified or specific sense, that is, (literally) to <i>moisten</i> (a part of one&rsquo;s person), or (by implication) to <i>stain</i> (as with dye): - dip.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G907/907\">G907</a>, <a href=\"#/G908/908\">G908</a>, <a href=\"#/G909/909\">G909</a>, <a href=\"#/G910/910\">G910</a>, <a href=\"#/G911/911\">G911</a>"}]}